    "I. INTRODUCTIONBusiness strategies and consumers' purchasing behaviors now heavily depend on customer reviews because of ecommerce's quick expansion in online shopping.",
    "Customer reviews offer helpful knowledge about different product aspects which includes their quality together with their price rating and assessment of appearance and service delivery.",
    "Businesses need ABSA as a fundamental technique to reveal precisely detailed sentiment data from product reviews which provides them valuable insights about customer feedback.",
    "The majority of ABSA research explores English texts but fails to address the substantial knowledge gap that exists for seventh most spoken language worldwide -Bangla.The research area of Aspect Sentiment Triplet Extraction (ASTE) for Bangla remains poorly studied even though major languages alongside English have made substantial recent progress.",
    "Span-based triplet extraction methods utilize text spans instead of words when extracting data and they demonstrate promising results when applied to English according to [1]."
